Privacy Policy for Naughty Bottle
Last Updated: February 22, 2026

This privacy policy governs your use of the software application Naughty Bottle (hereinafter "Application") for mobile devices.

1. Data Collection and Usage
Our Application uses third-party services that may collect information used to identify you. We use Unity Ads as our advertising provider. Unity Ads may collect data such as:

Device identifiers (IDFA for iOS, GAID for Android)

IP address

Game session activity

This data is used solely to provide personalized advertisements and analyze game performance.

2. Cookies and Consent
We implement a Consent Management system to comply with GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation) and CCPA (California Consumer Privacy Act). When you start the game, we ask for your consent to use cookies and device IDs for advertising purposes. You can change your preference at any time within the Application settings.

3. Age Restriction
Naughty Bottle is intended for users aged 18 and older. We do not knowingly collect personal identifiable information from children under 13. If we discover that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, we immediately delete this from our servers.

4. Security
We value your trust in providing us your personal information, thus we are striving to use commercially acceptable means of protecting it. But remember that no method of transmission over the internet, or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

5. Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at: icebreakerstudios.app@outlook.com
